    <section class="card">
      <h2>EEOC Complaint Checklist</h2>
      <p>Use this to track your progress. Your selections are saved only on this device.</p>

      <label class="step"><input type="checkbox" data-k="file"> <div><strong>File an EEOC Charge</strong><small>Submit online, by mail, or in person at an EEOC office.</small></div></label>
      <label class="step"><input type="checkbox" data-k="evidence"> <div><strong>Provide Supporting Evidence</strong><small>Emails, notes, witness names, documents.</small></div></label>
      <label class="step"><input type="checkbox" data-k="respond"> <div><strong>Respond to Information Requests</strong><small>Watch for EEOC communications and reply promptly.</small></div></label>
      <label class="step"><input type="checkbox" data-k="mediation"> <div><strong>Participate in Mediation (if offered)</strong><small>May resolve the case faster without full investigation.</small></div></label>
      <label class="step"><input type="checkbox" data-k="investigation"> <div><strong>Investigation</strong><small>Documents, interviews, and possible site visit.</small></div></label>
      <label class="step"><input type="checkbox" data-k="final"> <div><strong>Final Determination / Right to Sue</strong><small>Results or a Notice of Right to Sue and deadlines.</small></div></label>

      <div class="controls">
        <button class="btn btn-primary" id="save">Save</button>
        <button class="btn btn-secondary" id="reset">Reset</button>
